# Cognitive/Layered — REST Client (VS Code: REST Client by Huachao Mao)
# Run worker: npm run worker:cognitive-layered (from repo root)

@base = http://localhost:3000
@workflowId = <paste workflowId from start response>

### Simple query (reactive / fast path)
POST {{base}}/workflows/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowType": "cognitiveWorkflow",
  "input": {
    "query": "What time is it?"
  }
}

### Complex query (deliberative / reasoning path)
POST {{base}}/workflows/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowType": "cognitiveWorkflow",
  "input": {
    "query": "Compare microservices vs monolith for a team of 5. Give pros and cons."
  }
}

### Get run status
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}

### Get run result (wait until status is COMPLETED)
GET {{base}}/runs/{{workflowId}}/result
